        "text_diGwHX": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>China is the world’s largest producer of consumer goods — and that’s exactly why we choose to work there. Real impact doesn’t come from avoiding global manufacturing; it comes from changing it. We partner with manufacturers who might otherwise rely solely on new, virgin materials, helping shift their processes toward recycled alternatives instead. Every partner we work with is required to supply <strong>GRS (Global Recycled Standard) certification</strong>, giving us confidence that the recycled materials used in our products are genuine, traceable, and responsibly sourced. For us, progress means influencing the biggest players — not opting out of the conversation.</p>"
